全方位財經大師

掌握金融脈動，拓展國際視野
歡迎加入臺大「財務金融實務研討」課程

    永遠站在世界尖端的花旗集團，憑藉累積多年的寶貴金融智慧，致力於提昇全球經濟，
成就客戶財富。在台灣，我們秉持回饋社會的熱誠，多年來投入智慧傳承的工作，
將花旗豐富的金融經驗與領導管理,，導入大學的知識殿堂，向下紮根，期待孕育台灣
未來的財經大樑。

    今年，花旗集團於台灣大學財務金融學系開設之「財務金融實務研討」課程已邁入第八個
年頭。除了持續分享花旗世界級的企業金融、消費金融與投資銀行外，並加入分析瞬息
萬變的經濟趨勢及電子商務等課程，引領你深入認識多元財經智庫。

    面對兩岸經濟愈來愈密切的發展，今年也再度推出「花旗金融實務課程兩岸交流
計畫」，獎勵表現傑出的同學赴中國大陸參訪，包括政府機構、台商企業及上海花旗銀行
，並與復旦大學的同學研討交流，創新思維 ，開拓國際視野 !

    我們將於2月23日盛大展開本課程, 敬邀傑出的新生代一同與世界接軌，豐富您的智
慧財庫 !

Learn Banking and Finance From Citigroup Professionals
Enroll in the "Citigroup University Lecture Series"

As a preeminent global financial services company, Citigroup is committed to
supporting projects and programs that forge closer connections with the
community. Since 1998, Citigroup has sponsored the "Citigroup University
Lecture Series" in which professionals and executives from different banking
disciplines within Citigroup meet with university classes to discuss their
areas of expertise and work experience. Our core curriculum lectures feature
talks by professionals from our corporate banking,
consumer banking, securities, and investment banking departments.

This year, we will continue to conduct the "Cross-Strait Students Exchange
Program " which aims to broaden the scope and vision of the students.
The outstanding students will be sent to Shanghai for a Citibank tour and
exchange program with the students from Fudan University.

The lecture series commences on February 23, connecting the students to the
continuously changing world of global business.
